# Review Query Patterns

IMPORTANT: review_id is not unique (789 dupes), 547 orders have multiple
reviews. Deduplicate or GROUP BY order when computing review metrics.

## Average review score (deduplicated)
```sql
SELECT ROUND(AVG(review_score::NUMERIC), 2) AS avg_score
FROM (SELECT DISTINCT order_id, review_score FROM reviews) r;
```

## Review score by category
```sql
SELECT t.product_category_name_english AS category,
       ROUND(AVG(r.review_score::NUMERIC), 2) AS avg_score,
       COUNT(*) AS reviews
FROM reviews r
JOIN orders o ON r.order_id = o.order_id
JOIN order_items i ON o.order_id = i.order_id
JOIN products p ON i.product_id = p.product_id
JOIN category_translation t ON p.product_category_name = t.product_category_name
WHERE o.order_status = 'delivered'
GROUP BY 1 ORDER BY avg_score DESC;
```

## Score distribution
```sql
SELECT review_score, COUNT(*) AS cnt
FROM (SELECT DISTINCT order_id, review_score FROM reviews) r
GROUP BY 1 ORDER BY 1;
```